# AI Knowledge Assistant

A production-style AI Knowledge Assistant built with ASP.NET Core 9 and Azure OpenAI.

## Features

- Clean Architecture
- Azure OpenAI Integration
- Dependency Injection
- REST APIs
- Swagger
- Configuration using Options Pattern

## Tech Stack

- ASP.NET Core 9
- C#
- Azure OpenAI
- HttpClient
- Dependency Injection

## Roadmap

- [x] Chat API
- [ ] Embeddings
- [ ] Vector Database
- [ ] RAG
- [ ] Streaming Responses
- [ ] Function Calling
- [ ] AI Agents
- [ ] Azure AI Search
- [ ] Redis Cache
- [ ] Application Insights

## Architecture

```
API
 ↓
Application
 ↓
Infrastructure
 ↓
Azure OpenAI
```
